videos.description: Albert Almanza draws the foul and gets the lucky bounce on the 3-point shot to get a 4-point play opportunity.
videos.headline: Almanza gets the lucky bounce for 4-point play opportunity

videos.description: Aamir Simms comes up big nailing a 3 pointer from deep to kill the momentum of Sam Houston State.
videos.headline: Simms nails 3 pointer to deflate Sam Houston State

videos.description: Chad Bowie puts up a wild layup around a defender and somehow gets it to fall.
videos.headline: Bowie gets circus shot layup to go
